reviews.comments:
Marcelo was a wonderful host! We had a great time at his place.
Advantages are:
1) Really close to subway;
2) Three stations away from the center of the city if you take express train;
3) Quiet place;
4) Laundy room in the basement;
5) Grossery store, pizza and donats 2 minutes away. Also try fish (shrimps) and chips in a place called "famous fish market";
6) Apartment itself is really nice, clean and big for NY. There's everything you need in it, otherwise Marcelo will be happy to help.
Marcelo is very nice guy, we felt really comfortable staying at his place.
